channel.title: [PZ] DalaCity
channel.description:
[center][font=verdana][size=24pt][b]Project Zeta: DalaCity[/b][/size][/font][/center]
[b]Progress:[/b] [b]Beta[/b] [b]Beta Release date:[/b] [b]15 September 2012[/b]
[size=18pt][b]Introduction:[/b][/size] We are here to present you DalaCity. This can be kept short, We aim to create a fun rsps, influenced by both the old rs06 feeling and the rsps spirit, and most important: centering the player and not donations. Therefor our goals are to create a lot like how it was in 06, but also implement originality. Because originality is something that seems to be dead in the rsps development scene apart from a few exceptions. On that donators will not get any advantages that could unstable the equal gameplay between P2P & F2P.
[size=18pt][b]Team:[/b][/size] RandQm: Programmer Mister Master (Master Lop): advertising, forums, data input (npcs, definitons) [b]We are still looking for some one that wants (and can) to do graphics. Add me on skype if you are interested: randqm13[/b]
[size=18pt][b]CheckList:[/b][/size]
[b]Skills:[/b]
[ul][li][b]Combat:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Rewrite combat from scratch. (range, magic, melee, prayer)[/li] [li]All special attacks with right effects.[/li] [li]All magic spells with right effects.[/li] [li]Full multi target spells[/li] [li]All bones bury-able[/li] [li]More correct prayer draining[/li] [li]Decent formulas[/li] [/list] [li][b]Runecrafting[/b][/li] [list] [li]All runes working with multiplying by level[/li] [/list] [li][b]Agility:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Unique usage of ticket system.[/li] [li]Barbarian, Pyramid & Gnome courses.[/li] [/list] [li][b]Thieving:[/b][/li] [list] [li]All stalls with right items - chances & timers.[/li] [li]All npcs with right items - chances & timers.[/li] [/list] [li][b]Herblore:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Identifying herbs[/li] [li]Making all potions with right ingredients[/li] [li]potion mixing[/li] [/list] [li][b]Crafting:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Tanning[/li] [li]Hide crafting[/li] [li]gem cutting[/li] [li]amulet making[/li] [/list] [li][b]Fletching:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Right interfaces[/li] [li]Arrows & stringing[/li] [/list] [li][b]Slayer:[/b][/li] [list] [li]No clue yet.[/li] [/list] [li][b]Mining:[/b][/li] [list] [li]All ores working with influenced mining timers[/li] [li]Random gems event[/li] [li]empty & respawning of rocks with the right timers[/li] [/list] [li][b]Smithing:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Smelting with interface[/li] [li]Smithing with interface[/li] [/list] [li][b]Fishing:[/b][/li] [list] [li]All fishes with item & bait requirements.[/li] [li]Influenced timers.[/li] [/list] [li][b]Cooking:[/b][/li] [list] [li]All fish cookable with interfaces & timers.[/li] [li]Baking with interfaces[/li] [/list] [li][b]Firemaking:[/b][/li] [list] [li]Clipped firemaking[/li] [/list] [li][b]Woodcutting:[/b][/li] [list] [li]All trees working with influenced timers[/li] [li]stumping & respawning with right timers[/li] [/list] [li][b]Farming[/b][/li] [list] [li]All plants working in growing stages, must be watered, timers.[/li] [/list][/ul]
[b]Minigames:[/b]
[ul][li]FightPits[/li] [li]Tzhaar[/li] [li]Pest Control[/li] [li]Duel Arena[/li] [li]Castle Wars[/li] [li]Party Room[/li] [li]Custom minigame[/li][/ul]
[b]Misc:[/b]
[ul][li]Quests[/li] [li]Load itemdefinitions, bonuses & requirements via XML[/li] [li]Anti-auto clicking system[/li] [li]Random events[/li] [li]Unique advanced jailing system[/li] [li]pking streak with anti cheat[/li] [li]All global changed objects (stumps ect..) visible for all players also at region changing and logging.[/li] [li]All pickables[/li] [li]Clipped player following[/li] [li]Clipped npcs, returning to spawnpoint when moved out due e.g. combat[/li] [li]SkillGuides[/li] [li]All potions working with right effects[/li] [li]All eatables[/li] [li]Traveling system with congifs[/li] [li]100% mithril seeds.[/li] [li]Dalacity points (unique ways to earn - secret until beta)[/li] [li]Switching[/li][/ul]
